					<h2>His Story</h2>
						<p>	
						Zak met Jessica during freshman year of college.
						When he first met her, she was not a Christian, but over 
						the course of sophomore year, God saved her and changed her 
						heart. Zak found that encouraging, and he kept it in
						the back of his mind that she was a godly, attractive sister.
					</p>
					<p>
						Jessica and Zak were friends in college, but didn't spend much
						time together until after graduating. They got to know
						each other better while running and eating Krispy Kreme
						together frequently (don't worry, not simultaneously) with
					 	friends. 
						</p>
					<p>
						Zak realized he really liked Jessica, and after praying and
						consulting people wiser than himself, he finally decided it was
						time to ask her out (and soon after, propose). You can read
						about that a few tabs over!
					</p>
